{"tid":2209982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：勞動人口跌幅超預期或成經濟增長障礙","createTime":"2020-09-20T05:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T07:54:05.000Z","uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7e97460d84581f784e155182d77d60b2691f50","tid":2209982,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光預期，未來數年的勞動人口會持續下跌，長遠可能會成為未來經濟增長的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光在網誌撰文，指今年上半年勞工市場受疫情打擊，勞動人口由去年約364萬下跌至354萬人，現時仍難估計影響何時消退。假如在這段時間，提早離開勞工市場的人在經濟復甦後不重投職場，香港的人力短缺情況會比早前估計更嚴重，甚至會為經濟復甦拖後腿。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前推算，2022至2027年間勞動人口每年平均減少0.6%，但今年6至8月的勞動人口按年下跌2.1%，已超過預期三年的跌幅；長遠而言，可能會成為未來經濟增長障礙。"},{"pid":"03fb5faa80dfca4ff0072d6247754b67df53b730","tid":2209982,"uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8757bc8f5f9dbeafefbcbef789454bfa40175130","tid":2209982,"uid":26061,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:30:27.000Z","msg":"又有藉口引入中國勞工"},{"pid":"60cf386b2e9e429b5b333d8b68bd725ab815b7f3","tid":2209982,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"因為香港好多人靠被動收入已經夠過活"},{"pid":"a044d0af5fee33ba18d2eb97f9cb6b37ffb81fbc","tid":2209982,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"XGZF諗下自己做咗乜好加速人口下跌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4dcb1ca75ac30520371fe7e083003fa8bc0ee1","tid":2209982,"uid":322130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:42:16.000Z","msg":"根本佢講撚哂，實情想人口大清洗換血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />溝淡真香港人"},{"pid":"b5818dc158a5c4ac31b03226940df96028e2232d","tid